#: ../../en/book/appc-webdav.xml:372
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A WebDAV application is a program that speaks WebDAV protocols with a WebDAV "
"server.  We'll cover some of the most popular programs with this kind of "
"WebDAV support."
