#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><sect1><sect2><para>
#: ../../en/book/ch01-fundamental-concepts.xml:380
msgid ""
"If the URL contains spaces, be sure to place it within quotation marks so "
"that your shell treats the whole thing as a single argument to the "
"<command>svn</command> program."
msgstr ""
"如果 URL 包含空格，一定要使用引号，这样你的脚本才会把它做一个单独的 "
"<command>svn</command> 参数。"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><sect1><sect2><para>
