"就像<command>svn status</command>，<command>svn add</command>和<command>svn "
"import</command>命令也会忽略匹配这个列表的文件，你可以用单个的<option>--no-"
"ignore</option>命令行参数来覆盖这个选项。"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><sect1><sect2><sect3><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: ../../en/book/ch07-customizing-svn.xml:630
#, fuzzy
