#: ../../en/book/ch07-customizing-svn.xml:639
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This instructs Subversion to automatically set properties on newly added or "
"imported files.  The default value is <literal>no</literal>, so set this to "
"<literal>yes</literal> to enable this feature.  The <literal>auto-props</"
"literal> section of this file specifies which properties are to be set on "
"which files."
