#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><sect1><sect2><para>
#: ../../en/book/ch07-customizing-svn.xml:877
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"On Windows, locale configuration is done via the <quote>Regional and Language "
"Options</quote> control panel item.  There you can view and select the values "
"of individual settings from the available locales, and even customize (at a "
"sickening level of detail) several of the display formatting conventions."
