msgid ""
"In this chapter, we explored Subversion's runtime configuration system and "
"other mechanisms by which users can control those configurable behaviors.  If "
"you are a developer, though, the next chapter will take you one step "
"further.  It describes how you can further customize your Subversion "
"experience by writing your own software against Subversion's libraries."
